<div class="wrapper main-pages center">
  <div class="page-wrapper">
    <div class="row row-centered">
      <div class="col-md-10 text-center col-centered">
        <div class="box title">
          <h2>Para teres uma pesquisa ainda mais personalizada, responde às seguintes questões.</h2>
          <p>Pode preencher ou editar o questionário mais tarde, através do seu perfil. </p>
        </div>

        <%= form_for @user, :url => "savePreferences?id="+@user.userID.to_s , method: :post do |u| %>
        <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
          <div class="panel-group" id="accordion">
            <div class="panel panel-default panel-preferences-d" id="panel1">
              <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title panel-preferences">
                  <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseOne">
                    Que tipo de ambientes te agrada mais?
                  </a>
                </h4>
              </div>
              <div id="collapseOne" class="panel-collapse collapse in">
                <div class="panel-body panel-pref-body">
                  <div class="row">
                    <% @ambianceTags.each do |tag| %>
                    <%= check_box_tag 'ambianceTags[]', tag.tagsID, @tag == tag %>
                    <%= tag.name %>&nbsp;
                    <% end %>
                  </div>
                  <div class="row btn-down-pref">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-default " data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseTwo">
                     <i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-down"></i>
                   </button>
                 </div>
               </div>
             </div>
           </div>
           <div class="panel panel-default panel-preferences-d" id="panel2">
            <div class="panel-heading">
              <h4 class="panel-title panel-preferences">
                <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseTwo">
                  Os teus estilos de música preferidos:
                </a>
              </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseTwo" class="panel-collapse collapse">
              <div class="panel-body panel-pref-body">
                <div class="row">
                  <% @musicTags.each do |tag| %>
                  <%= check_box_tag 'musicTags[]', tag.tagsID, @tag == tag %>
                  <%= tag.name %>&nbsp;
                  <% end %>
                </div>
                <div class="row btn-down-pref">
                  <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseThree">
                   <i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-down"></i>
                 </button>
               </div>
             </div>
           </div>
         </div>
         <div class="panel panel-default panel-preferences-d" id="panel3">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title panel-preferences">
              <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseThree">
                Estás à procura de eventos em que áreas?
              </a>
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div id="collapseThree" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body panel-pref-body">
              <div class="row">
                <% @categories.each do |category| %>
                <div class="col-md-2 ">
                  <%= check_box_tag 'categories[]', category.categoryID, @category == category %>
                  <%= category.name %>&nbsp;
                </div>
                <% end %>
              </div>
              <div class="row btn-down-pref">
               <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseFour">
                 <i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-down"></i>
               </button>
             </div>
           </div>
         </div>
       </div>
       <div class="panel panel-default panel-preferences-d" id="panel4">
        <div class="panel-heading">
          <h4 class="panel-title panel-preferences">
            <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseFour">
              És uma pessoa que prefere eventos mais diurnos ou noturnos?
            </a>
          </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseFour" class="panel-collapse collapse">
          <div class="panel-body panel-pref-body">
            <div class="row">
              <label for="eventTime"></label>
              Diurnos <i class="fa fa-sun-o"></i> <%= radio_button_tag 'eventTime', "dayTime", @eventTime == "dayTime", :checked => false %> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
              Noturnos <i class="fa fa-moon-o"></i> <%= radio_button_tag 'eventTime', "nightTime", @eventTime == "nightTime", :checked => false %> 
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <%= button_to "Preencher mais tarde", :back, :class => 'btn btn-default sub3-light'%>  <%= u.submit 'Submeter', :class => 'btn btn-default sub3' %>
      <% end %>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>







